The video was published on Facebook on D: 2020, and has a duration of 4 minutes and 53 seconds.
The caption of the Facebook post: translated from simplified Chinese, describes a US astronaut jumping from 39 kilometers in space towards Earth at supersonic speed.
The video was shared on multiple platfor: including Facebook, Twitter, and Weibo, with similar claims.
A keyword search based on the text: RED BULL STRATOS" found that the jumper in the video is actually Austrian skydiver and pilot Felix Baumgartner, not a US astronaut.
